name: Trademark Motion Activated LED Strip Light
description: This innovative TG Motion Activated 6 LED Strip Light allows you to illuminate any area without the hassle of cords and plugs. With six super bright white LEDs even the darkest corner of your home will be well lit. Adhesive backing or screw mounting options allow you to place your light quickly and easily! The motion activated technology provides 20 seconds of bright light per activation.
